snippet.title: A public letter to AMBER HEARD from a survivor of DV
snippet.description:
Welcome all, 

This video is a #PublicLetterToAmberHeard from a #SurvivorofDV.
Contained within the video is the letter and below are links related to the video.
Please excuse our poor editing skills as photo editing isnt our strong suit. 

Thank you to @steviejraw, @SpirituallyEmpoweredCoaching and @shelbysoup, for all the help and info provided to us to help this process go ahead.

Our twitter is @Justiceforsurv4

UK Court Documents are available at www.nickwallis.com

And importantly our Change.org petition which you can find at http://chng.it/RGQt4CnxPD.

#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #DomesticViolenceKnowsNoGender #JusticeForSurvivors
